--   вҠЁ question is scenario-based, not a definition request вҶ’ вң“
--     (scenario: "you and a colleague both working... for the past two days")
--   вҠЁ target-understanding names a specific concept being tested вҶ’ вң“
--     (names: "commit graph topology", "divergent histories", "fork in history")

