-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- OBSERVATIONS (v0.2-aware)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў= obs-guard-clause-skipping
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "v0.2 GUARD CLAUSE VALIDATED: design-followup's guard (understanding-level != 'solid') correctly skipped the cell in iteration 2 when the student demonstrated solid understanding. Without the guard, design-followup would have fired uselessly вҖ” attempting to redesign a question for a student who already understands. The guard clause saved one LLM call and prevented the вҠўвҲҳ loop from receiving a confusing В§ask' rewrite it would never use. Guard-induced вҠҘ propagated cleanly because no downstream cell depended on design-followup's outputs at that point."

вҠў= obs-accumulate-mode
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "вҠўвҠў ACCUMULATE MODE PRODUCES COMPLETE MISCONCEPTION LOG: spawn-remedials fired 3 times across iterations, producing remedial-0 (timeline), remedial-1 (pull), remedial-2 (timestamps). Because accumulate mode preserves cells across iterations, collect-remedials received ALL misconceptions ever discovered, not just the latest. This is pedagogically correct вҖ” a teaching record should capture the entire learning journey, including misconceptions that were already resolved. Replace mode would have discarded earlier remedials, losing the learning history."

вҠў= obs-aspirational-oracles-teaching
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "v0.2 ASPIRATIONAL ORACLES IN PEDAGOGICAL CONTEXT: ask's oracles (scenario-based, names specific concept) passed in all iterations вҖ” but if they had failed in iteration 0, the вҠўвҲҳ loop would have continued anyway. The oracles describe good teaching practice (the ASPIRATION), while the вҠўвҲҳ until condition (understanding-level = 'solid') is the OPERATIONAL gate. This is exactly right for teaching: a question can be imperfect (fail oracle) but still advance understanding. The вҠўвҲҳ loop tolerates pedagogical missteps and corrects through iteration."

вҠў= obs-misconception-convergence
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "MISCONCEPTION COUNT AS CONVERGENCE SIGNAL: iteration 0 found 2 misconceptions, iteration 1 found 1, iteration 2 found 0. The monotonically decreasing misconception count is a natural convergence metric that emerges from the teaching loop without being explicitly tracked. The вҠўвҲҳ loop's until condition (understanding-level = 'solid') captures the endpoint, but the misconception trajectory reveals the SHAPE of convergence. This suggests misconceptions[] length could serve as an auxiliary until condition in teaching programs."

вҠў= obs-given-optional-dep
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "v0.2 given? TOLERATES EDGE CASE: design-followup uses given? for evaluateвҶ’misconceptions because when understanding-level is 'solid', the misconceptions list is empty (not вҠҘ, but [])). In this program the given? is defensive rather than necessary вҖ” misconceptions is always bound (even if empty). But if evaluate had been modified to yield вҠҘ for misconceptions when correct=true (a valid alternative design), given? would prevent design-followup from blocking. The given? annotation communicates INTENT: misconceptions are supplementary input, not a hard requirement."

вҠў= obs-wildcard-quiescence
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "WILDCARD + ACCUMULATE REQUIRES QUIESCENCE AWARENESS: collect-remedials uses wildcard remedial-*вҶ’corrected-understanding. With accumulate mode, the match set grows across вҠўвҲҳ iterations. collect-remedials cannot safely fire until the вҠўвҲҳ loop terminates AND all matched cells freeze вҖ” otherwise it would collect a partial set. The runtime must track вҠўвҲҳ termination to know when the wildcard match set is final. This is a subtle interaction between three v0.2 features (wildcard deps, accumulate mode, вҠўвҲҳ lifecycle) that the spec should document explicitly."

вҠў= obs-file-scope-recovery
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "v0.2 FILE-SCOPE вҠЁ? WITH partial-accept(best): the file-scope recovery policy was never triggered because all oracles passed and вҠўвҲҳ converged within max 5. But the partial-accept(best) exhaustion handler is well-suited to teaching: if the student never reached 'solid' understanding after 5 iterations, accepting the best version of ask (the most targeted question) is a reasonable degradation. For teaching, partial success IS success вҖ” even an imperfect teaching session advances understanding."
